article.headline: Nelson scores 21 as Utah Valley takes down UTEP 89-60
article.description: — Dominick Nelson had 21 points in Utah Valley's 89-60 victory against UTEP on Saturday night.
article.linkText: Nelson scores 21 as Utah Valley takes down UTEP 89-60
article.story: OREM, Utah -- — Dominick Nelson had 21 points in Utah Valley's 89-60 victory against UTEP on Saturday night. Nelson added eight rebounds for the Wolverines (2-0). Tanner Toolson scored 16 points while going 5 of 10 (4 for 7 from 3-point range) and added six rebounds. Hayden Welling shot 5 of 8 from the field, including 3 for 4 from 3-point range, and went 2 for 3 from the line to finish with 15 points, while adding three blocks. Devon Barnes led the way for the Miners (1-1) with 13 points and two steals. Otis Frazier III added 11 points and three steals for UTEP. Ahamad Bynum also had nine points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
